              <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">2</div><h3>Search Bond Series</h3><p>Look up available tax-free bond series on NSE/BSE by searching for NHAI, REC, PFC, or IRFC tax-free bond symbols. Compare YTM, maturity dates, and prices.</p></div>
              <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">3</div><h3>Place Buy Order</h3><p>Place a limit order at your desired price. Since these bonds trade infrequently, patience may be needed. Consider placing orders close to the current offer price for faster execution.</p></div>
